snippet.title: Star Stuff Teaser Trailer
snippet.description: Star Stuff is a puzzle automation game that mixes programming & real-time shenanigans. Play as Mija (me-ha), a cosmic employee on their first day at a star factory. Automate your own bots, interact in real time with bot actions to solve mind-bending puzzles, and save the ever-expanding universe!
